{"tid":1018020,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"直屬上司無封利是比我，係咪走得？","createTime":"2019-02-12T01:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T17:28:21.000Z","uid":11270,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"38bcfee083b538d9c8aa709245c259d669267c9a","tid":1018020,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"先利申，自己未結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說返咗工幾日，都收到好多同事，甚至唔同部門既呀頭封利是比我，唯獨是無收到自己直屬呀頭果封<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以為佢可能姑9寒唔派，點知比我發現隔離部門既同事竟然收到我呀頭封利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問下佢係咪想炒我魷魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又或者想我唔撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0664a595175f536e0e0efc1e9e1db18a659e4f7","tid":1018020,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"快係佢炒你前辭職"},{"pid":"e1b5fe51bec7b1d1f976dd61063acf10bb7bbb24","tid":1018020,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"可能唔記得咗"},{"pid":"daee85c1aa102f96e46b4c1b399ded9171bc5ccb","tid":1018020,"uid":11270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1b5fe51bec7b1d1f976dd61063acf10bb7bbb24","tid":1018020,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"可能唔記得咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:10:06.000Z","msg":"唔會掛，佢得3-4條嚫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a9ad6b4c32aaeac04e543918a1fb51c08aecd4","tid":1018020,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"都走咯，當面問佢啦"},{"pid":"e10c225fc224d5699c45dd7af1a81297b4beaf7d","tid":1018020,"uid":11270,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51a9ad6b4c32aaeac04e543918a1fb51c08aecd4","tid":1018020,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":